{"tid":1990131,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★北角行人天橋火警露宿者---11年前由內地來港 4名子女居住內地","createTime":"2020-04-26T12:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T05:09:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8b6a98ef7ef8a6c86e6d7dde322f85499726a9dc","tid":1990131,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T12:49:11.000Z","msg":"在北角糖水街行人天橋露宿1年半，一場大火令她家當盡失，無處容身。一班主要操英語的志願團體ImpactHK義工，雖然與一口濃重福清話的麗姐語言不通，仍努力透過身體語言，少量廣東話及普通話，了解麗姐的苦況及提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n麗姐1<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1年前由內地來港</span>投靠家住北角的女兒，惟女兒有家庭無能為力，提及家人時她一度落淚稱：「好頭痛、好痛苦。」<br />\n<br />\n麗姐的故事，由11年前說起，她育有5名子女，其中4<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">名子女居住內地</span>，2009年麗姐隻身來港，本打算投靠家住北角的女兒，惟女兒有家庭，無力照顧，麗姐無奈淪落街頭，約1年半前開始在北角糖水街行人天橋露宿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/465677/%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E7%81%AB%E8%AD%A6-%E9%9C%B2%E5%AE%BF%E8%80%85%E9%BA%97%E5%A7%90%E6%8B%BE%E7%B4%99%E7%9A%AE%E7%B6%AD%E7%94%9F-%E5%AE%B6%E7%95%B6%E7%9B%A1%E5%A4%B1-%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%8B%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F465677%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%25A7%2592%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E9%259C%25B2%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%25BA%2597%25E5%25A7%2590%25E6%258B%25BE%25E7%25B4%2599%25E7%259A%25AE%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%2595%25B6%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25A4%25B1-%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%258A%25A9&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4NqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=52e10fd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/465677/%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E7%81%AB%E8%AD%A6-%E9%9C%B2%E5%AE%BF%E8%80%85%E9%BA%97%E5%A7%90%E6%8B%BE%E7%B4%99%E7%9A%AE%E7%B6%AD%E7%94%9F-%E5%AE%B6%E7%95%B6%E7%9B%A1%E5%A4%B1-%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%8B%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9</a>"},{"pid":"6f4cee480f0cce036ff77c0a0840598a962a8aab","tid":1990131,"uid":19454,"like":7